"Mixer, Citadel, and Galley) and then `upgrade the data plane "
"</docs/setup/upgrade/cni-helm-upgrade/#sidecar-upgrade>`_ to `Istio "
"1.1.16 </news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.16>`_ or later."
msgstr ""

